---
title: `$to::title()`
description: Convert file name, HTML string or plain text into `Title Case`.
...

~~~ .php.xmp
To::title($in);
~~~

**Example:**

~~~ .php
$test_1 = To::title('foo-bar-baz');
$test_2 = To::title('<p><strong>foo</strong> bar <em>baz</em></p>');
$test_3 = To::title('foo bar baz');
~~~